# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# FlockOS .gitignore
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── OS / Editor artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# ── Backup / temp files ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.bak
*.tmp
*.log
*.md.bak

# ── Google Apps Script backend files ─────────────────────────────────────
# .gs files are deployed via the Apps Script editor, not git.
*.gs

# ── Documentation text files ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Internal docs with sensitive references; not for public repos.

# ── Sensitive docs / architecture (Covenant-era) ────────────────────────
# Keep architecture and runbook material local-only by default.
Covenant/Testimony/
Covenant/Storehouse/
Testimony/Architecture/
Testimony/Runbooks/
Testimony/Migration/
Storehouse/
FlockOS/Tools/Build Documents/Flock Docs/

# ── Internal tools folder — never publish ────────────────────────────────
# Contains deployment guides, admin credentials, API URLs, build scripts.
FlockOS/Tools/Flock Secrets/
FlockOS/Tools/Flock Deployments/
FlockOS/Tools/Production Notes/
FlockOS/Planning/
# Canonical path after Covenant migration
Covenant/Courts/TheTabernacle/Tools/Flock Secrets/
# Catch-all for per-church tool secrets folders
**/Tools/Flock Secrets/
# ── Internal reference docs ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Large citation/reference markdown — useful locally, not for the repo.
\#\ Code\ Citations.md
\#\ Code\ References.md

# ── Firebase CLI artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────
.firebase/
flockchat-public/

# ── Node / build artifacts (future-proofing) ─────────────────────────────
node_modules/
FlockChat-Functions/node_modules/
.env
.env.*

# ── Capacitor build output ───────────────────────────────────────────────
www/
ios/
android/

# ── Python build tools ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
CurrentFBPW.json

# ── Security hardening (explicit secret patterns) ───────────────────────
# Catch secret files even if moved outside expected folders.
**/*firebase-adminsdk-*.json
**/*service-account*.json
**/*private-key*.json
**/CurrentFBPW.json

# Keep secret vaults local-only across any future folder reshuffles.
**/Secrets/**

# Architecture split safety: keep heavy local archives out of commits.
Architechtural Docs/Storehouse/**

# Planning / operational docs are local-only by default.
**/*-Runbook*.md
**/*-Plan*.md
**/*Action Items*.md

# ── Local-only utility scripts ───────────────────────────────────────────
# One-off scripts (e.g. Firestore checks, data migrations) — local only.
FlockOS/Tools/Flock Scripts/H-Check_Firestore.py
check_*.py
migrate_*.py
Icon

# New Covenant — local-only architectural notes
New_Covenant/Architechtural Docs/

# Entire architecture split tree is local-only and should never be tracked.
Architechtural Docs/

# Local-only symlink to gitignored Architechtural Docs (was breaking GitHub Pages tar --dereference)
Covenant/Scrolls/ChurchRegistry
